OL,3,CMan charged following fatal A7 crash
OL,4,Cnear Ashkirk
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man has been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a fatal crash in the
OL,8,FScottish Borders.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, 15 August, 2023, 64-year-
OL,11,Fold Yvonne Nichol died following a
OL,12,Fthree-vehicle crash on the A7 near the
OL,13,FAshkirk junction.
OL,15,FThe 30-year-old had previously been
OL,16,Farrested and released pending further
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,19,FA report will now be submitted to the
OL,20,FProcurator Fiscal and he is expected
OL,21,Fto appear at court at a later date.
