OL,6,FYvonne Nicol was the driver of a
OL,7,FVauxhall Astra and following the
OL,8,Fcrash, she was taken to Borders
OL,9,FGeneral Hospital where she later died.
OL,11,FA 65 year old man who was a passenger
OL,12,Fin the same car suffered serious
OL,13,Finjuries.
OL,15,FThe 71-year-old female driver of a
OL,16,FNissan Juke was taken to the Royal
OL,17,FInfirmary of Edinburgh for treatment
OL,18,Fto serious injuries.
